title: Main Street New Jersey Community Boundaries
name: Main Street New Jersey Community Boundaries
description:
Main Street New Jersey provides selected communities with technical assistance and training of proven value in revitalizing historic downtowns. The program helps municipalities improve the economy, appearance and image of their central business districts through the organization of local citizens and resources.
This dataset was developed to aid in identifying the Main Street program focus areas. The areas delineated by these boundaries are currently in the Main Street program.

author.source: New Jersey Office of Smart Growth
